39:45.674 --> 39:47.468
I can't believe that was this morning.

39:47.551 --> 39:49.845
Ah, just another day at the office.

39:49.929 --> 39:51.472
(Nic chuckles softly)

39:51.555 --> 39:52.848
-So...
-Hmm.

39:52.932 --> 39:55.226
So we're gonna start telling
everyone we're engaged, huh?

39:55.309 --> 39:58.521
Let's shout it from the rooftops.

39:58.604 --> 40:00.439
