40:02.525 --> 40:05.403
Oh, and in the spirit of being open,

40:05.486 --> 40:06.987
I have a confession.

40:07.071 --> 40:09.573
I, um, may or may not
have eaten the chocolates

40:09.657 --> 40:10.825
