40:10.908 --> 40:12.368
-You didn't.
-I did.

40:12.451 --> 40:13.994
-Aw...
-(laughs)

40:14.078 --> 40:17.748
-Well, I have nothing to confess.
-Oh, really? Nothing?

40:20.000 --> 40:21.836
Fine.

40:24.296 --> 40:28.217
That diamond on your ring is fake.
It's cubic zirconium.

40:28.300 --> 40:30.719
-Really?
-Yes.

40:30.803 --> 40:32.805
Huh, it looks so real.

40:32.888 --> 40:34.765
Well, in that case, you want it back?

40:34.849 --> 40:36.851
-Wait...
-I mean, if it's fake...

40:36.934 --> 40:38.144
-What?
-We don't have to get married.

40:38.227 --> 40:39.979
-Honestly. (laughing)
-No. No, no, no, no, no.

40:40.062 --> 40:42.231
I'm kidding, I'm kidding, I'm kidding.

40:45.860 --> 40:47.611
I love it.

